# CLAIMSUTRA PROJECT STRUCTURE

## Root Directory
/v4-improved homepage layout/
- `package.json` - Main project configuration, dependencies, and scripts
- `package-lock.json` - Auto-generated file for npm dependency versioning
- `.gitignore` - Specifies files to be ignored by Git
- `README.md` - Project overview and documentation
- `.env` - Environment variables (should be in .gitignore)
- `.eslintrc.js` - ESLint configuration for code quality
- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript configuration (if applicable)

## Source Code
/src/
- `index.js` - Application entry point
- `App.js` - Main application component

## Components
/src/components/
- `/common/` - Reusable UI components following Single Responsibility Principle
  - `Button.js` - Custom button component
  - `Input.js` - Custom input field component
  - `Modal.js` - Reusable modal component
  - `Card.js` - Card container component
  - `Loading.js` - Loading spinner/indicator
- `/layout/` - Layout components
  - `Header.js` - Application header component
  - `Footer.js` - Application footer component
  - `Sidebar.js` - Sidebar navigation component
  - `MainContent.js` - Main content wrapper

## Homepage Components
/src/components/homepage/
- `Hero.js` - Hero section for homepage
- `Features.js` - Features section showcasing key benefits
- `Testimonials.js` - Customer testimonials section
- `CTASection.js` - Call to action section
- `InfoCards.js` - Information cards section

## Pages
/src/pages/
- `HomePage.js` - Improved homepage implementation
- `ClaimsPage.js` - Insurance claims page
- `ProfilePage.js` - User profile page
- `LoginPage.js` - User login page
- `RegisterPage.js` - User registration page

## Services
/src/services/
- `api.js` - API service following Dependency Inversion Principle
- `auth.js` - Authentication service
- `claims.js` - Claims-related service
- `storage.js` - Local storage service

## Utilities
/src/utils/
- `validators.js` - Input validation helpers
- `formatters.js` - Data formatting utilities
- `constants.js` - Application constants
- `helpers.js` - Common helper functions

## Assets
/public/assets/
- `/images/` - Image files
- `/icons/` - Icon files
- `/fonts/` - Custom fonts

## Styles
/src/styles/
- `global.css` - Global CSS styles
- `variables.css` - CSS variables for theming
- `components/` - Component-specific styles
  - `button.css`
  - `form.css`
  - `modal.css`

## Documentation
/guide/
- `STRUCTURE` - This file, documenting the project structure
- `project-documentation.md` - Detailed project documentation
- `api-docs.md` - API documentation
- `dev-guide.md` - Developer guide and best practices
- `user-guide.md` - End-user documentation

## Configuration
/config/
- `webpack.config.js` - Webpack configuration
- `routes.js` - Application route definitions

## Tests
/tests/
- `/unit/` - Unit tests for components and services
- `/integration/` - Integration tests
- `/e2e/` - End-to-end tests